ActsAsCommentable
=================

Aims to be a full-fledged threaded comments system. 

Borrows liberally from acts_as_nested_set, acts_as_authentable and other versions of acts_as_commentable.


Instructions
=======

1. Run: script/generate acts_as_commentable
2. Run: rake db:migrate to create the comments table
3. Add acts_as_commentable to any class you'd like users to be able to comment on



